967
00:55:38.936 --> 00:55:41.091
Menangis, minta tolong?

968
00:55:42.019 --> 00:55:42.996
Bodoh.

969
00:55:43.020 --> 00:55:45.061
Kita akan ditembak mati.

970
00:55:45.478 --> 00:55:46.829
Penjaganya adalah militer.

971
00:55:46.853 --> 00:55:48.120
Mereka akan mengerti kode Morse.

972
00:55:48.144 --> 00:55:49.995
Mari kita kirim SOS dengan kode Morse.

973
00:55:50.019 --> 00:55:50.983
SOS terlihat bagus.

974
00:55:51.314 --> 00:55:53.148
Hei! Kenapa kamu
berkedip terus-menerus?

975
00:55:55.061 --> 00:55:56.978
