01:06:18.478 --> 01:06:21.519
Mamet, kakekmu
pasti bangga padamu.

1090
01:06:21.728 --> 01:06:22.769
Terima kasih.

1091
01:06:23.644 --> 01:06:24.686
Sama-sama.

